title: Episode 83: Election Recap
description:
Ms. Pat and Deon had a wild weekend in Colorado... No, maybe it was Chicago? Oh! It was Atlantic City! They recap the outcome of the 2020 Election. We end with a discussion of Chris's privates after he grinds the show to a screeching halt.
